<L>To &s;hut out virtue, and unfold tho&s;e gates</L>
<L>That Heaven it&s;elf had barr'd again&s;t the lu&s;ts</L>
<L><PB N="162" REF="026674_0162_0FD1567E63C9FCC0">Of avarice and ambition. Soft and &s;weet,</L>
