<L>See nodding fore&s;ts on the mountains dance,</L>
<L><PB N="174" REF="026674_0174_0FD156996329A9C8">See &s;picy clouds from lowly Sharon ri&s;e,</L>
<L>And Carmel's flow'ry top perfumes the &s;kies!</L>
</LG>
<LG N="5">
<HEAD>5.</HEAD>
<L>Hark! a glad voice the lonely de&s;ert cheers;</L>
